<br />
So since a monk could tank almost as well as a warrior (almost, with the<br />
higher DPS of the monk being the reason monks would sometimes be chosen over<br />
warriors as the group's tank), that's justification for reducing their<br />
tanking ability to under all other melee classes?  Don't believe the hype.<br />
There was one reason and one reason only for the monk nerf.  Too many monks.<br />
It was population control, pure and simple.<br />
