rogues are better.  (My rogue was regularly backstabbing for around a<br />
100 at lvl 20, and had weapons that had damage procs as well).  A<br />
Warrior with reasonable armour and a Centi Shortsword (200plat or less<br />
on my server) can take and dish out damage that renders me<br />
superfluous, AND they can Taunt, too.<br />
<br />
Rogues are better scouts, and THE best corpse-draggers in the<br />
business, too.  Feign Death??  Give me the Sneak/Hide combo any day of<br />
the week to walk past lethal mobs, and give me Evade in combats, and<br />
you can keep the Feign death  :D  Mend skill?  Don't make me laugh....<br />
I'd rather have a 30 point Heal Spell I could count on!<br />
<br />
I have a Beastlord - who wants a lvl 20 monk when you could have a lvl<br />
20 Beastlord??  You get a pet that can proc for damage thrown in with<br />
a Beastlord at that level...<br />
<br />
I have to say that I rarely, if ever, come across a monk these days,<br />
at least on my server.<br />
<br />
