that can reduce atk and speed?  Come on, we've all seen Kung Fu and<br />
how he could drop a guy with one shot.  Crouching tiger hidden dragon<br />
anyone?<br />
<br />
I guess what I'm saying is the Berserker never should have been made,<br />
the monk should have recieved those abilities.<br />
