&quot;soft cap&quot; is the point where added AC lends greatly deminishing results in<br />
neutralizing the ATK value of mobs.  Through the different expansions, the<br />
ATK of mobs has generally increased to the point in GoD now that tanks still<br />
get significant returns on AC above 2000.<br />
