&gt; inflict a potential 225 damage on the WIELDER :D  Sure, the mobs in<br />
&gt; the area took damage, but I'd rather my monk didn't risk electrocution<br />
&gt; every melee!!!  Gonna look like a scene out of a Jackie Chan movie -<br />
&gt; comic monk exits stage right - clothing scorched and tattered and hair<br />
&gt; smoking]<br />
