&gt; As for pulling, forget it - it isn't worth the mana to heal my monk,<br />
&gt; to be honest.  My mighty range weapons may irritate the mob into a<br />
&gt; charge, but arrows and spells are better.<br />
&gt;<br />
&gt; My &quot;mighty&quot; hand-to-hand skills can do some damage, but nukes and<br />
&gt; rogues are better.  (My rogue was regularly backstabbing for around a<br />
&gt; 100 at lvl 20, and had weapons that had damage procs as well).  A<br />
&gt; Warrior with reasonable armour and a Centi Shortsword (200plat or less<br />
&gt; on my server) can take and dish out damage that renders me<br />
&gt; superfluous, AND they can Taunt, too.<br />
&gt;<br />
